	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Recepi tuas, chare frater; excusatio plena est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2" cert="high">Aaroviensia</placeName> finita dudum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio in his actum de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646" cert="high">Glaronensibus</placeName> et concilio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Concilium progreditur; accepi sessionem primam habitam 26. februarii; 2. decreta est maii 14.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Citantur in concilium sub salvo conductu omnes docti, qui libros scripserunt et damnati sunt in catalogo Pauli 4.; incipiunt enim concilium ab illis libris, qui falsam doctrinam invexerunt etc.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> res summo versatur in discrimine.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Guysianus</persName> recta digressus ex colloquio <placeName type="citizen_name">Tabernensi Alsatico</placeName> invasit ecclesiam <placeName type="auto_name">Vasseii</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name">Campania</placeName>; dicuntur in coetu trucidati ad 150, vulnerati supra 200; mox direpta sunt ipsorum omnia.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Questi sunt de iniuria in aula; variae fuerunt sententiae; tandem instituta inquisitio.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim nunciatur <persName type="auto_name">Guysianum</persName> instructum equitatu forti progredi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Denunciat regina: ni dimittat exercitum, fore ut iram regis incurrat; ille excipit: "Si venero, excusabo me ut nil me[lius]."</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Regina cum rege dicitur <persName type="auto_name">Aureliam</persName> se rece[pisse], <persName type="auto_name">Guysianum</persName> vero festinare cum exercitu [Lut]etiam.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec inde scribuntur 17. m[artii].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">[Quid inte]rea factum sit, novit dominus...</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt, qui dic[ant...] et legatum pontificis <placeName type="citizen_name">Ferrariensem</placeName> cardinalem impetras[se, ut] et legati mittantur in concilium et episcopi.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Also wachst des tüfels werck.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Min herren schri[b]end den schidorten den tag zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l970" cert="high">Einsidlen</placeName> ab; dann <placeName ref="l781" cert="high">Ury</placeName> embüt gen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2450" cert="high">Schwytz</placeName>: ir aman <persName type="auto_name">Imm Hoff</persName>, der ein zuͦgsatzter, sye abgescheiden mitt todt; der ander zuͦgsatzt zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2450" cert="high">Schwytz</placeName>, aman <persName type="citizen_name">In der Halden</persName>, wil warten, biß man setzt ein andern zuͦgesatzten zuͦ imm.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der kranck zuͦgsatzt von <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaris</placeName>, der <persName type="citizen_name">Tschudi</persName>, seckelmeister, ist tödtlich ouch kranck xin, aber wider uff.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Da schript <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2450" cert="high">Schwytz</placeName> gen <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaris</placeName>, sy söllind den tag nitt besuͦchen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaris</placeName> schript minen herren, die den andern schidorten etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich acht, wenn der tag fürggangen, hätte der bischoff von <placeName type="auto_name">Chum</placeName> uns concilij wägen geladen; wirts filicht sunst thuͦn.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">3. aprilis 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus, qui semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fabulas puto, quae de monte sparguntur; <foreign xml:lang="de">[w]irt ettwas anders sin etc.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, domino suo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555" cert="high">Wintherdur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Vermerk von <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">A. Blarers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Remitte.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
